Map Remade By: BabyFace
www.KrackHouse.net

Created from scratch while looking
at both CS and CSS Hammer.
Textures taken from original map
and HL1 WAD files.
Some PC Textures from 
de_cyberwar_beta2 By:Razorzone|Dude


Original Map By: Ryan "NEMESIS" Gregg
Textures by: Baby Killer & Nemesis

Counter-Terrorists: Rescue the
scientist hostages from their
terrorist captives, the scientists
hold the key to returning anyone
back to real life size.

Terrorists: Prevent the capture of
the scientists and eliminate all
threats. 

Other Notes: There are 4 hostages.
Beware of all enviromental
threats.
